    "Thus, ML-guided discovery of environmentally friendly electrolyte materials will be significant for battery recycling.",
    "For example, nonflammable and environmentally friendly ionic liquid electrolytes show great promise as next-generation electrolytes for advanced batteries under extreme conditions.",
    "Thus, it is valuable to construct a database based on these green electrolytes and further guide the optimized protocols and parameters to recycle or even rebuild the batteries in the future.",
